The paper deals with image classification, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on Non-I.I.D. image classification, which is a problem in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the construction of a dataset, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
